<style>body{height:95vh;display:grid;place-content:center;background-color:rgba(230,230,230,.74)}.box{position:relative;top:50%;transform:translate(0,-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;width:50vw;height:80vh;justify-content:space-evenly;padding:30px;background:#0fcdff;background:linear-gradient(128deg,rgba(15,205,255,1) 0,rgba(122,255,247,.9976365546218487) 18%,rgba(211,240,156,1) 49%,rgba(233,216,80,1) 74%,rgba(255,179,0,1) 100%);border-radius:30px;box-shadow:5px 5px 20px #979797;transition:1s;animation:dropDown ease 1.5s}.forbidden__img{width:45%}.status__content{padding:20px}.status__code{font-family:"Courier New",Courier,monospace;font-size:4rem;font-weight:900;color:#d80c0c;transition:.8s}.status__info{font-family:"Franklin Gothic Medium","Arial Narrow",Arial,sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;color:#e00e0e;transition:.8s}.status__message{font-family:"Courier New",Courier,monospace;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;width:321px;color:#474747;transition:.8s}@keyframes dropDown{0%{top:-120%}50%{top:15%;transform:rotate(3deg)}100%{top:0;transform:rotate(0)}}@media (max-width:1500px){.box{width:60vw}}@media (max-width:1200px){.box{width:70vw}}@media (max-width:1000px){.box{flex-direction:column-reverse;width:50vw;height:60vh;padding-top:0}}@media (max-width:640px){.forbidden__img{width:75%}.status__content{padding:0}.status__code{font-size:3.3rem;margin-left:20px}.status__info{font-size:25px;margin-left:20px}.status__message{font-size:18px;width:50vw;margin-left:20px}}</style><div class=box><img alt=Forbidden class=forbidden__img src="data:image/png;base64,"><div class=status__content><h1 class=status__code>HTTP 403</h1><p class=status__info>FORBIDDEN<p class=status__message><i>OOPS!!!</i> You don't have permission to access on this server</div></div>
